net.floodlightcontroller.core.internal

Class OFChannelInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.floodlightcontroller.core.internal.OFChannelInfo

  • public class OFChannelInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Basic information that OFChannelHandler attaches to the netty channel via Channel#setAttachment(Object), mainly for the purpose of being able to log the connection information.
